 intersections in the city of Ahmedabad in India. A\ndetailed evaluation of SILSTM on the SkyEye dataset shows that unsafe\n(collision-prone) interaction trajectories can be effectively detected at\ndifferent intersections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Dec 2019 16:35:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-11"}
