 very massive thick disc and an underdeveloped thin disc, whose\ngrowth ended prematurely due to the exhaustion of the cold gas likely because\nof environmental effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Dec 2019 18:55:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Mar 2020 04:14:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-01"}
