of roughly 1-5 virial radii from the most massive halos in our sample\n($>$10$^8~h^{-1}$M$_\\odot$), as these tend to be embedded deeply within the\ncosmic web.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Dec 2019 19:01:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-12"}
