-ray observations, and assuming the existence of the ALP to\nalleviate the tension is not required in a statistical sense, thus the excess\nover the EBL models is less likely to be a new EBL component.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Dec 2019 13:52:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Jan 2020 09:18:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 6 Jun 2020 12:17:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2021 00:35:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-21"}
